55 numerator of which is the average number of eligible migrant students enrolling in that
56 school after the final FTE count as required in subsection (a) of Code Section 20-2-160 but
57 prior to the end of the same academic year and the denominator of which is the average
58 total number of eligible migrant students enrolling after the final FTE count as required in
